    <div class="container-einstein">
      <p>A<span><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p2nwdS3ia24"> "light clock"</a></span> is a thought experiment Einstein used to explain time dilation: think a light beam -a photon- bouncing between two mirrors in perfect opposition. Or are they…? Read more about Albert’s idea<span><a href="/einsteins-light-clock" target="_blank"> here</a></span></p>
